(5413, 'Gemzar 1 gm i.v. vial', 'جيمزار 1 جم فيال', '1294', '1,682', 'Gemcitabine', 'Vianax - greece > eli lilly', 'Vial', 'فيال', '', 'Antineoplastic', '1 gm', 'Gemcitabine is a chemotherapeutic agent used as monotherapy or in combination with other anticancer agents. 
